        <item>
            <title>【評測】Nikon Z50II 入門無反數碼相機，實試秒速開機 + 極速對焦 + 香港人像風景試相</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/27/nikon-z50ii-review/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nikon-z50ii-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/27/nikon-z50ii-review/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 14:15:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相機測試]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nikon Z50II]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277615</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>數碼相機愈來愈先進，物體辨識、人眼自動對焦系統發展成熟，更逐步下放到入門相機。今次介紹的 Nikon Z50II 作為 Nikon 最新入門無反相機，全面升級使用 Expeed 7 影像處理引擎，操作非常爽快之餘，人臉、人眼辨識、物體辨識的速度極快，準確度也非常高，配合 Nikon 一向對相機機身堅固程度的執著，成為了價格相宜、堅固好手感，而且非常容易上手、應用的數碼相機麼。以下小編會為大家詳細介紹，這部入門機有甚麼原因，可以成為好多人每日帶出街，常備隨時使用的實用相機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03965-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03965-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03965-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03965-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC_0510" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54168049350/in/album-72177720322198912" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54168049350_6b1ac5fc4d_b.jpg" alt="DSC_0510" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC_0461" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54167592311/in/album-72177720322198912" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54167592311_532541271a_b.jpg" alt="DSC_0461" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>機身設計：適中體積與舒適手感</h2><p>Z50II 的機身相比首代 Z50 稍微增大，重量增加了約 100 克，總體機身重量為約 550 克。雖然相比同類型的 APS-C 影像無反相機，它的體積偏大，但這也帶來了更好的握持感。無論是使用輕便的 16-50mm Kit 鏡頭，還是稍重的 50-250mm 長焦鏡頭，Z50II 的手感都讓人滿意，即使長時間手持拍攝，依然能夠保持舒適。好多入門機一拿上手，你會覺得「啊，這部是入門機，但它夠便宜就忍一下」；但今次這部 Z50II 機身擁有 Nikon 傳統的硬朗設計，整體質感也超越了一般入門級數。可以説除了它的 APS-C 影像感應器或許不如全片幅之外，拿上手與其他中階機沒有太大差別。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03928-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03928-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03928-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03928-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03944-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03944-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03944-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03944-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03944.jpg"><br /></a>▲配合 Kit 鏡機身極為輕巧</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03940.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277654" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03940-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03940-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03940.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03937.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277694" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03937-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03937-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03937.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03963.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03963-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03963-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03963.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03933.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03933-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03933-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03933.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲機身較一般入門機大，因此握感也會較好</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03934-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277696" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03934-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03934-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03934-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03935.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277664" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03935-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03935-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03935.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲即使是入門機，LCD 顯示器大小仍有 3.2 吋，而且可反出來自拍</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03941.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03941-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03941-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03941.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲擁有 0.39 吋電子觀景器，以入門機來説相當大，而且光亮度是 Z50 兩倍，睇得十分舒服</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03974-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03974-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03974-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03974-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Z50II 繼續內置閃光燈，保留傳統</p><h2>觀看 Nikon Z50II 的測試相片相簿</h2><p>我們在 Flickr 上載了今次測試相片，本文所有測試相片都可點擊打開大圖片。而在下面連結的相簿中，還有更多測試相片，每張都可放大觀看，也可下載相片到電腦，自行鑑賞相機實際相片效果。</p><p>＞＞＞＞<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/albums/72177720322198912/">點擊打開 Nikon Z50II 的 Flickr 相簿</a>＜＜＜＜</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024112764939-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277641" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024112764939-694x536.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="536" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024112764939-694x536.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024112764939-scaled.jpg 1164w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
